query:
SELECT EXISTS (
               SELECT 1
               FROM tabular ta
               WHERE ta.warehouse_id = $1 AND (fs_location = ANY($2) OR
                      -- TODO: revisit this after knowing performance impact, may need an index
                      (length($4) < length(fs_location) AND ((TRIM(TRAILING '/' FROM fs_location) || '/') LIKE $4 || '/%'))
               ) AND tabular_id != $3
           ) as "exists!"
